entries.title: Facebook Starts Effort to Boost Equity in Housing Ads
entries.description: Machine-learning technology was deployed by Meta Platforms as part of a settlement regarding housing discrimination charges against the company.

entries.title: Beijing Signals Tech-Firm Crackdown May End
entries.description: A top Chinese official said authorities have wrapped up investigations into the financial businesses of several internet companies.

entries.title: Sam Bankman-Fried's Lawyers Are Veterans of  Ghislaine Maxwell, 'El Chapo' Cases
entries.description: FTX founder’s defense team is led by former federal prosecutors with experience in high-profile cases, including Ghislaine Maxwell and ‘El Chapo.’

entries.title: New York City Scrambling to Find Space for EV Chargers
entries.description: To meet ambitious plans to phase out combustion engines, the city must install thousands of chargers by 2030 to boost electric-vehicle ownership
